 Nigerian singer Barry Jhay has been arrested in Ghana, in connection to the death of his label boss, Karshy Gordon. Kashy Godson died in the early hours of today, March 7, in Ghana. Kashy died hours after he had a serious fight with Barry. The fight left Barry Jhay wounded as seen in a video earlier posted by the singer. Unconfirmed reports claim Kashy committed suicide, others alleged he was pushed to his death by cultists. The singer has been arrested in Ghana in connection to the death of kashy . View this post on Instagram A post shared by Olorisupergal (@olorisupergal)